{"surah": 108, "verses": [{"id": 1, "text": "إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed><tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َآ</tajweed> أَعْطَيْنَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>كَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْكَوْثَرَ <span class=end>١</span>"}, {"id": 2, "text": "فَصَلِّ لِرَبِّكَ وَ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>نْحَرْ <span class=end>٢</span>"}, {"id": 3, "text": "إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ شَانِئَكَ هُوَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْأَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>بْ</tajweed>تَرُ <span class=end>٣</span>"}]}